01:38:11,619 --> 01:38:14,748
...and he wants to help you
to pay your medical bills...

1018
01:38:14,922 --> 01:38:19,656
...and to offer my counsel
in your defense if you need it.

1019
01:38:20,294 --> 01:38:22,388
Why would he do that?

1020
01:38:22,563 --> 01:38:25,931
Because you would sign this testimony
which states that...

1021
01:38:26,100 --> 01:38:30,401
...Ronald Smythe
threatened Jonas' life...

1022
01:38:30,571 --> 01:38:33,666
...and forced him to rob
the Silvermans at gunpoint.

1023
01:38:33,841 --> 01:38:37,676
- That's bullshit.
- You don't know that for sure, do you?

1024
01:38:38,078 --> 01:38:40,047
You're such a coward.

1025
01:38:40,214 --> 01:38:42,046
- Miss Tanner.
- Go fuck yourself.

1026
01:38:42,216 --> 01:38:44,242
- Will you step outside, please?
- Jonas.

1027
01:38:44,418 --> 01:38:47,786
Just give us a minute.
Just take a walk.

1028
01:39:02,136 --> 01:39:07,598
You remember you asked me one time
how I wound up on the street?

1029
01:39:09,643 --> 01:39:11,009
Yeah.

1030
01:39:13,814 --> 01:39:15,976
It's because my dad kicked me out.

1031
01:39:17,351 --> 01:39:18,717
Why?

1032
01:39:21,789 --> 01:39:23,724
Because we hate each other.

1033
01:39:26,827 --> 01:39:31,993
One night he took a swing at me
after I got the tattoo...

1034
01:39:32,166 --> 01:39:36,604
...and he hit me so fucking hard
it landed me in the hospital for a week.

1035
01:39:39,940 --> 01:39:42,068
Sounds like an asshole.

1036
01:39:43,077 --> 01:39:44,636
He is.

1037
01:39:46,246 --> 01:39:48,408
That's why you gotta sign
this document...

1038
01:39:48,582 --> 01:39:50,710
...and have him pay
for your medical bills.

1039
01:39:53,687 --> 01:39:55,986
I should probably sign it.

1040
01:40:01,595 --> 01:40:03,359
But I can't.

1041
01:40:04,565 --> 01:40:07,057
I'm not lying or cheating anymore.

1042
01:40:08,035 --> 01:40:10,197
I'm telling the fucking truth in court.

1043
01:40:11,405 --> 01:40:13,465
You're making a mistake.

1044
01:40:15,309 --> 01:40:17,403
That's what I always do.

1045
01:40:29,723 --> 01:40:31,715
Jonas Trumball?

1046
01:40:33,027 --> 01:40:38,398
Fine of $50,000 and 200 hours
of community service.

1047
01:40:39,833 --> 01:40:42,564
I'd say you got off easy, Jonas.
Wouldn't you?

1048
01:40:42,736 --> 01:40:44,762
Thank you, Your Honor.

1049
01:40:44,938 --> 01:40:46,634
Get out of my courtroom.

1050
01:40:52,146 --> 01:40:54,115
Kelly Tanner.

1051
01:40:54,882 --> 01:40:56,077
Yes?

1052
01:40:56,784 --> 01:41:01,552
Breaking and entering, theft,
six months sentence, no parole.

1053
01:41:01,722 --> 01:41:04,749
Pleaded guilty. Turned yourself in.

1054
01:41:06,160 --> 01:41:07,822
Do you think you belong here?

1055
01:41:08,662 --> 01:41:10,460
It's the penalty, isn't it?

1056
01:41:10,631 --> 01:41:14,432
For breaking the law, for lying,
for stealing?

1057
01:41:14,601 --> 01:41:16,570
Just let me pay it.

1058
01:41:17,438 --> 01:41:18,997
Okay.

1059
01:41:19,306 --> 01:41:21,605
See your parole officer
on your first day.

1060
01:41:21,775 --> 01:41:24,745
He or she can lay out the obligations
of being on parole.

1061
01:41:24,912 --> 01:41:27,643
They're easy. Stay out of trouble.

1062
01:41:27,815 --> 01:41:29,215
I will.

1063
01:42:24,905 --> 01:42:26,430
Kelly.

1064
01:42:38,118 --> 01:42:40,212
Oh, I missed you.

1065
01:42:40,387 --> 01:42:43,289
- Michael--
- Hey, it's okay.

1066
01:42:43,457 --> 01:42:45,949
It's okay, we'll figure it out, okay?